; Regression test for GitHub issue #1004
; "Assertion failure when parsing ledger file with whitespace-only line"
;
; When a whitespace-only line (e.g., a line containing only a single space)
; appears between a periodic transaction (~) and the next transaction,
; ledger crashed with an assertion failure in parse_post():
;   "Assertion failed: *line"
;
; The fix adds a missing empty-line check in parse_posts() that matches
; the pattern already used in parse_xact() and automated_xact_directive().

~ Monthly
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash
 
2013/01/01 Some Transaction
    Expenses:Food    $5.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
              $-5.00  Assets:Cash
               $5.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
